##Setup

Clone the project:

    git clone <repo path>

Setup a virtual env

    virtualenv ve

Start Virtual ENV

    source ve/bin/activate

GOTO Directory

cd

Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.pip

##Prerequisites :
1. npm install grunt
2. npm install grunt-cli
3. npm install bower
4. bower install bootstrap

```
$ npm install
$ bower install
```

Create a DB rpc

Copy local settings

cp GraphProject/settings/local_settings.py.back GraphProject/settings/local_settings.py

Run Migration

python manage.py migrate

Start Server

python manage.py runserver 8000

## For hosting the html page:
 1. Install XAMPP server from :
        https://www.apachefriends.org/download.html

 2. Copy the 'app' folder to applications/xampp/htdocs/
 3. Start the xampp server and check if Apache server is running. Configure to run on 8088
 4. Start the UI on localhost:8088/app/


